    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "THE COCKEYED BALLAD SPACE AGE SONGS by Mollie Thompson",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "SPACE-TALK",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "There's a cockeyed feeling in the world today",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "That power politics is here to stay.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "But China, Russia and the U.S.A.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "Boy-don't let them fool you!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "Take a look at this world of ours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "Just one mud ball in the sea of stars.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "Other planets have no color-bars,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "'Cause they've got perspective.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "Yanks and Ruskies put men into space,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "But it's all a mad politician's race.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "One-up-manship in this Year of Grace.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "It makes you giggle.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "The population stands and stares,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "While men in capsules explore upstairs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "text": "Why we can't even manage our own affairs!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "Some cheek-colonization!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "Besides, they've got people on Venus and Mars.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "They got lads and lasses and ma's and pa's.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "text": "And they've got better transport than four-wheel cars.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "Have you ever seen 'em?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "Those Flying Saucers whisking through our skies",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "text": "Must take some power to make them rise.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "But government departments just hide their eyes.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "text": "And call them meteors!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "text": "With all the lies that they print and shout,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "The general public's got its work cut out-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "text": "Figuring what it's all about.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "text": "But just you keep on trying.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 97,
      "text": "I suppose you know why I'm telling you this,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "text": "So you won't shriek or shake your fist",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "text": "When you discover Martians do exist!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "text": "They're real nice fellows.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 101,
      "text": "I know, 'cause I met one a week ago!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 102,
      "text": "His ship came down for an hour or so.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 103,
      "text": "He talked to me, but then he had to go.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 104,
      "text": "I'm real interested I was!",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "text": "Got brothers on Venus and Saturn, it seems-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 106,
      "text": "Fly their ships on magnetic beams.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 107,
      "text": "They wear one piece suits-you can't see any seams;",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "text": "The powers that be will tell us we're alone.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 110,
      "text": "They'll tell us that in space we are unique;",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 111,
      "text": "On this little desert island we call Earth",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 112,
      "text": "The human race is just a kind of freak.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 113,
      "text": "When we send our envoys into space",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 114,
      "text": "There'll be a smile upon this planet's face.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 115,
      "text": "There's another human race; it's very true!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 116,
      "text": "For they just never go to war.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 117,
      "text": "And they cannot interfere.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 118,
      "text": "This is by Universal Law.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 119,
      "text": "The spaceman's message to us all",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 120,
      "text": "Is based on how to banish fear,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 121,
      "text": "And if we only understand,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 122,
      "text": "We will find heaven here.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123,
      "text": "We must rely on war,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124,
      "text": "We never will be happy here.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 125,
      "text": "While this world's economy",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 126,
      "text": "Is based on hardship, strife and fear.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 127,
      "text": "How do they live without a war",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128,
      "text": "In their lands of milk and honey?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129,
      "text": "They don't need economy,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 130,
      "text": "Because they don't use any money!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 131,
      "text": "They cannot give us any ships,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 132,
      "text": "But we must try and build our own.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 133,
      "text": "But they are waiting right out there,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 134,
      "text": "Oh, my friends, we're not alone!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 135,
      "text": "How do they go at such great speed,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 136,
      "text": "And vanish then without prediction?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 137,
      "text": "Because they use free energy,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 138,
      "text": "And there isn't any friction.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 139,
      "text": "Brother have you seen their ships?",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 140,
      "text": "Sisters have you seen them glow,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141,
      "text": "As they dance and hover in the sky,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 142,
      "text": "And make our fastest jets look slow?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    }
  ],
